title: Doctor Who Complete Season 04, 1966-1967, Patrick Troughton
description:
All 43 episodes of the 1966/67 season of Doctor Who, featuring the First Doctor (William Hartnell) and the Second Doctor (Patrick Troughton), and his companions: Polly, Ben Jackson, Jamie McCrimmon, and Victoria Waterfield. 

This is the most heavily reconstructed season, with no complete serials. Reconstructions use photographs taken on set and recovered segments of footage, along with the audio recordings of the episodes, to recreate missing episodes. Visual and audio quality varies depending on the reconstruction.

Container: mp4
Video: H.264
Audio: AAC
Display: 640x480
